Linux Kernel 2.6.x Panic Module Installation Guide
==================================================
- Untar panic-0.0.1.tgz to /tmp
- Change directory to /tmp/panic
- Edit the line 2 of Makefile, modify the KSRC to the directory 
  where your kernel source is. (like /usr/src/linux)
- "make"
- "insmod panic.ko", then the system will be panic.
 
